Package maze

Interface MazeSolution

  • public interface MazeSolution
    A MazeSolution holds a Maze and a ListInterface of Rooms that are an the order which can be used to reach a Room that is an exit.
    Author:
    jcollard

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      Maze getMaze()
      Returns the Maze that this MazeSolution solves.
      ListInterface<Room> getSolution()
      Returns a ListInterface containing Rooms in an order which can be used to reach an exit.
